{
  "stem": "22734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's about taking another five minutes or maybe eight minutes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And now when I walk through Prague, it's all there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It didn't change.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, it's-- it's-- it's-- it's difficult to relate to that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We would pick up their lunch and feed them lunch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I loved this Danny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I-- I sort of made up my mind that if I ever have a boy, he'll be Danny.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was-- that was Danny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in-- I think it was already in October of '40, they-- yes, it was in the fall of '40, they called the first transport.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no Terezin yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They called twice, two and a half thousand people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they were told just to take 50 kilos with them, anything that they carry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had to assemble at the Prague Exhibition Grounds, which was a-- a big sort of glass palace which had a floor, sort of a warehouse down.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not on the outskirts of Prague.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was really basically in a very good part of Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they just stood there and-- in two days, they were transported to Lodz, the Lodz ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And out of those 5,000 that were transported in '40, 11 came back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I know a girl who came back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She lives in Calgary now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so when you-- that was the first inclination we had that there will be-- that we'll be transported somewhere.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they called-- then they-- and how they called, and you got sort of a piece of paper like a telegraph strip where you said you should present yourself there and there with the 52 kilos that you can carry.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or maybe it was just your name and your assigned number.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
